Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9)

Package: minisphere
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: JavaScript game engine
 minisphere is a lightweight re-implementation of the Sphere game engine
 originally developed by Chad Austin which sports better performance, more
 features, and command-line development tools such as a debugger and
 packaging compiler.
